        <name>next_subpass</name>
        <qualifiedname>d3d::next_subpass</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Advances to next subpass. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Increases subpass number and executes necessary synchronization as well as binding, described for this subpass</para>
<para><ref refid="structViewport" kindref="compound">Viewport</ref> is reset to render area on every call <simplesect kind="note"><para>Must be external synced (GPU lock required) </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="warning"><para>Will assert-fail if there is no subpass to advance to </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="warning"><para>Will assert-fail if called outside of render pass </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
